  <p>Read more about creating NHS <a href="https://www.england.nhs.uk/nhsidentity/identity-guidelines/organisational-logos/">organisational logos in the NHS England identity guidelines</a>.</p>
  <p>The organisational logo is an SVG (scalable vector graphic) and you can change the organisation name and descriptor in the code. Longer organisation names should be split onto 2 lines.</p>
